346
00:36:11,984 --> 00:36:26,892
[SPEAKER_07]: So number 6 requires the School Building Committee to comply with MSBA guidelines and align with but is not bound by the Medford School Committee policy BDF, which is our process to appoint advisory committees to the school committee.

347
00:36:27,313 --> 00:36:29,254
