471
00:50:45,857 --> 00:50:53,882
[SPEAKER_01]: So we're not going to be bringing them up to speed on decisions and things we've already done and are completed from nine months or three years ago.

472
00:50:54,283 --> 00:50:58,926
[SPEAKER_01]: We're going to be bringing them up to speed on the things that are being worked on at the moment.

473
00:50:59,706 --> 00:51:02,128
[SPEAKER_01]: So maybe that isn't as big of a lift, actually.

474
00:51:02,888 --> 00:51:04,790
