00:51:49,020 --> 00:51:56,827
[SPEAKER_04]: It's almost like a moving target, and it's going to be very difficult to predict that.

481
00:51:57,919 --> 00:52:21,548
[SPEAKER_04]: So I think as the application goes forward to really ask the members of the community that are interested if they could really do a due diligence and just say they really want to commit to this process so that we have a real working group that is going to be able to contribute for the duration of the project.

